Openmoko Mail is a mail client software, based on [http://tinymail.org libtinymail].

== Overview ==

It is currently using a GTK+ User Interface and supports:
simple configuration (Adding/Editing account info) interface. Multiple e-mail account handling, mail writing sending, replying and forwarding and of course deleting. Attachment adding, getting and forwarding. 

== GSOC 2008 ==

By the end of GSOC 2008 it is expected to support also :
-Attachment choose by file chooser (similar to [[Media Player]]'s) <br>
-Choosing email from contact's book. <br>
-GPG signing and encrypting of the mails. <br>
-Displaying HTML messages. <br>
-SMS messages managment. <br>


